  }
  footer.colophon a { color: var(--ink-soft); }
  footer.colophon a:hover { color: var(--regulatory-red); }
</style>

<div class="layout">

  <header class="masthead">
    <div class="brand"><a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">Hamburger Business Review</a></div>
    <div class="meta">Vol. I · Filed via Vibes DIY</div>
  </header>

  <div class="filing-bar">
    <span>Form 10-K · For Fiscal Year Ending: Whenever You Get Hungry</span>
    <span class="stamp">Unaudited</span>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Hero / Spotlight ── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="lede">
      <span class="kicker">Spotlight Filing · Order 10-K</span>
      <h1>The business of <em>your</em> burger.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Most people review a fast-food meal in a star rating. The serious reader files
        a 10-K. Paste in your order, scan the receipt — get back a parody annual report
        with revenue, COGS, risk factors, MD&amp;A, and a shareable cover sheet. The
        spotlight tool of seven, made for people who already think of their drive-thru
        habit as a portfolio.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{apps.0.author}}/{{apps.0.slug}}">File Your First 10-K</a>
        <a class="btn-secondary" href="#gallery">See the Other Six</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="filing-card" aria-label="Sample 10-K filing">
      <span class="stamp-corner">Specimen</span>
      <h3>Filing · Wendy's Run · 11:47 PM</h3>
      <dl>
        <dt>Revenue</dt><dd>$11.42</dd>
        <dt>COGS (cal)</dt><dd>1,840</dd>
        <dt>Segment Mix</dt><dd>Burger 68% · Fry 22% · Drink 10%</dd>
        <dt>Sauce Reserves</dt><dd>Ghost Pepper × 4</dd>
        <dt>Risk Factors</dt><dd>Late-night staffing · Frosty machine</dd>
        <dt>Forward Outlook</dt><dd>Heartburn anticipated Q1.</dd>
      </dl>
      <div class="mda">
        Management notes a difficult quarter for the Jr. Bacon segment but reaffirms
        guidance on the Baconator line. The board remains optimistic.
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Statline ── -->
  <div class="statline">
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Filings</div>
      <div class="v">Seven</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Persistence</div>
      <div class="v">Fireproof</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Skin</div>
      <div class="v">Proof Sheet</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="k">Stance</div>
      <div class="v">Not Reviews</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Section header ── -->
  <div class="section-hdr" id="gallery">
    <h2>Other Filings on the Wire</h2>
    <span class="label">// supporting tools</span>
  </div>

  <section class="apps">
    {{#each apps}}{{#unless spotlight}}
      <article class="app {{#if live}}app--live{{else}}app--pending{{/if}}">
        <div class="head">
          <span class="num">№ {{num}} · {{slug}}</span>
          <span class="status">{{#if live}}Live{{else}}Pending{{/if}}</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
        <p class="tagline">{{tagline}}</p>
        <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
        {{#if live}}
          <a class="shot" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="{{title}} screenshot"><img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"/></a>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Open</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/clone/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Clone</a>
            <a class="btn btn-remix" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Remix</a>
          </div>
          <a class="prompt-link" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">↳ start fresh from this prompt</a>
        {{else}}
          <div class="shot"><div class="shot-placeholder">Awaiting Deploy</div></div>
          <div class="ctas ctas--single">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">Start From Prompt</a>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </article>
    {{/unless}}{{/each}}
  </section>

  <section class="epilogue">
    <h2>// editor's note</h2>
    <p>
      Fast food isn't a category to <em>rate</em>. It's a category to <em>file against</em>.
      Seven tools — each one treats your order, your habit, or your operator the way a
      serious reader of the business would. Clone any one of them and turn the joke into
      your own franchise.
    </p>
    <div class="byline">— Filed via Vibes DIY · clone the kit, remix the doctrine</div>
  </section>

  <footer class="colophon">
    <span>vibes.diy · <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">homepage</a> · <a href="/dating.html">dating</a> · <a href="/college.html">college</a> · <a href="/expressions/">expressions</a></span>
    <span>// 30 —</span>
  </footer>

</div>
